import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['speed'], bins=30, color='blue', alpha=0.7)
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['speed'].median():.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('Wind Speed')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind speed?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    scatter = ax.scatter(data['dir'], data['speed'], c=data['dirCat'], cmap='viridis', alpha=0.5)
    plt.xlabel('Direction')
    plt.ylabel('Speed')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between wind speed and direction?', wrap=True)
    legend1 = ax.legend(*scatter.legend_elements(), title="Direction Categories")
    ax.add_artist(legend1)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['dir'], bins=25, color='blue', alpha=0.7, edgecolor='black')
    plt.xlabel('Wind Direction (degrees)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind direction?', wrap=True)
    plt.axvline(data['dir'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['dir'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    dirCat_counts = data['dirCat'].value_counts()
    dirCat_counts.plot(kind='bar', color='c', edgecolor='k')
    
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind direction categories?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Wind Direction Categories')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend(['Wind Direction Categories'])
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    heatmap_data = data.pivot_table(index='latitude', columns='longitude', values='speed', aggfunc='mean')
    sns.heatmap(heatmap_data, cmap='coolwarm', annot=False)
    plt.title('What is the spatial distribution of wind vectors?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Longitude')
    plt.ylabel('Latitude')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
